ay grow, when embedded in a\nhomogeneous under-saturated soft elastic medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Sep 2014 01:35:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Oct 2014 01:01:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-14"}
