onances on the conductance plateaus of a clean QPC. We argue that\nFabry-Perot-type resonances occur generically if the electrostatic potential of\nthe QPC generates a flatter-than-parabolic barrier top.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Sep 2014 12:41:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-11"}
