 level width. For completeness, we\nalso compute the shot noise and discuss the resulting Fano factor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Sep 2014 14:21:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Aug 2015 13:42:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-26"}
